  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra"><img src="/media/13049751/view-of-the-andorra-pyrenees.jpg" alt="Andora Pyrenees" data-udi="umb://media/df71f6aff178478aa6061919831b31db" /></a><br />
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra">Andorra</a></strong> today is a modern and extensive ski region that has changed almost beyond recognition from just a few decades ago. The vast transformation, means Andorra still remains a hidden gem within the ski industry. It offers fantastic value for money skiing and snowboarding, due to its duty-free status, meaning food and drinks are far cheaper than neighbouring countries. As a result of a multi-million pound facelift, the resorts have moved more upmarket with a whole new generation of state-of-the-art lifts and snow-making facilities ensuring fantastic conditions on the slopes and easy access throughout the ski area. Hotels have also been under renovation, many with great leisure facilities.</p>
<p><strong>We operate in 2 ski regions ;</strong> </p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59}" title="Pas de la Casa">Pas de la Casa</a></strong> - <strong>Good for…</strong> <em>après-ski, beginners &amp; groups</em></p>
<ul>
<li>Larger of the two regions known as the Granvalira super-ski area.</li>
<li>With over 200km of slopes. Pas de la Casa is the highest resort in Andorra with slopes as high as 2640m and has a correspondingly good snow record.</li>
<li>Both resorts offer convenient and quick access to the slopes.</li>
</ul>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7}" title="Arinsal"><strong>Arinsal</strong></a><strong> - </strong><strong>Good for…</strong><em>beginners, families &amp; après-ski</em></p>
<ul>
<li>Favourite for beginners and intermediates as there are lots of sunny days and well-prepared confidence-building runs</li>
<li>Wide range of activities to do in resort such as tobogganing, dog sledding and snowmobiling.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Fantastic offers for Andorra</strong></h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Free Lift Passes for Children</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra"><img src="/media/13078370/children-skiing.jpg" alt="Children skiing in Andorra" data-udi="umb://media/7f1920a6dc6a4353b2a563bc23e85392" /></a></p>
<p>We understand that ski holidays can be expensive for families and so we are happy to be able to offer free lift passes for children in <a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra">Andorra</a> when parents pre-book their lift passes.</p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Arinsal - </strong>free under 16 years </li>
<li><strong>Soldeu &amp; Pas de la Casa</strong> - free under 12 years</li>
</ul>
<p><a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Find out more"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Ski Inclusive</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f308314cef634f59a84f5eeed76d74d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f308314cef634f59a84f5eeed76d74d8}" title="Ski Inclusive Holidays"><img src="/media/13078371/398274-1.jpeg" alt="Skiing in Andorra" data-udi="umb://media/f199d71c6afc43c8881ee687cdb82a6c" /></a></p>
<p>This can be added onto any resort/hotel in Andorra for great value ski holidays.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Ski inclusive includes;</strong> 6 day lift pass, ski/board &amp; boot hire &amp; lunch vouchers.</li>
</ul>
<p><a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/f308314cef634f59a84f5eeed76d74d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f308314cef634f59a84f5eeed76d74d8}" title="Find out more "><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a>Convenient Flight Times</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra"><img src="/media/13078398/shutterstock_1418458319.jpg" alt="Convenient Flight Times to Andorra" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Outbound flight times;</strong> All of our flights are morning arrivals into Barcelona Airport between 10:30-11:30.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Inbound flight times;</strong> All of our flights depart Barcelona Airport around lunch time on your return.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Flights available from;</strong> Gatwick, Luton, Bristol, Manchester &amp; Edinburgh.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Find out more"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Top Hotel offers for Andorra</strong></h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a>Hotel Princesa &amp; Diana Parc<br />Arinsal</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7}" title="Arinsal"><img src="/media/13078392/princesa-parc-hotel.jpeg" alt="Hotel Princesca &amp; Diana Parc in Arinsal" data-udi="umb://media/6b352001202c4f7e893e2e39508a3d39" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">This luxury resort hotel offers excellent facilities including a Wellness Spa, games room, restaurant and bar. <strong>Ski Inclusive </strong>is already included in the price of this holiday<strong> PLUS free </strong>drinks at the hotel bar.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7}" title="Arinsal"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a>Hotel Himalaia<br />Soldeu</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/5336cc6eed49460eaff8868e5ea21b28" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5336cc6eed49460eaff8868e5ea21b28}" title="Hotel Himalaia"><img src="/media/13072690/fachada-exterior.jpg" alt="Hotel Himalaia in Soldeu" data-udi="umb://media/2ea9de6cc1fc41829fdb6b2a3c2c0eb2" /></a></p>
<p>A popular hotel in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a> and less than 2 minutes' walk to the Soldeu gondola. The wellness centre is included in the holiday price with Inghams.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/5336cc6eed49460eaff8868e5ea21b28" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5336cc6eed49460eaff8868e5ea21b28}" title="Find out more">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a>Hotel Piolets<br />Soldeu</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2034c79978494d81ba4c2622018d7288" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2034c79978494d81ba4c2622018d7288}" title="Hotel Piolets"><img src="/media/13078388/26_pioletsparkspa.jpg" alt="Hotel Piolets in Soldeu" data-udi="umb://media/9eaa5d7e8f7b45e2ae5f351c9bb19b0b" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Superb location in the very heart of Soldeu just next to the gondola. Excellent leisure facilities and bar with terrace offering scenic piste views.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/2034c79978494d81ba4c2622018d7288" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2034c79978494d81ba4c2622018d7288}" title="Hotel Piolets">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g12">
<p><strong style="font-size: small;">Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<div style="font-size: small;">
<ul>
<li>Free lift passes for children: Valid when parents pre-book their lift passes with Inghams</li>
<li>Ski inclusive: Valid as an add-on in any hotel in Andorra. Prices may differ depending on the hotel/dates. Included in price for Hotel Princesa &amp; Diana Parc only.</li>
<li>All prices are per person and include flights, transfers, 7 nights accommodation and meals as indicated.</li>
<li>When clicking through to the property pages the prices you see are the live and accurate prices.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
